        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Yun Jin A, a woman in her mid-30s, has never experienced a successful relationship. After being dumped countless times for her clumsy and reckless behavior, she is heartbroken when a man breaks up with her, calling her as unappealing as bland devil's-tongue jelly.\n\nThen, Seo Jun Hui, her childhood friend's younger brother, reappears. Now an attractive and confident man, he surprises Jin A, and she begins to feel that this time, she\n\nmay finally find love.",
